HEADWORD: Fulgurate
<hw>Ful"gu*rate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>fulguratus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>fulgurare</ets> to flash, fr.
